# Digital Loyalty Card App — Design Document

**Date:** 2026-02-25
**Status:** Approved
**Approach:** React Native (Expo) + Supabase + Next.js

---

## 1. Product Vision

A B2B2C digital loyalty platform enabling any type of merchant to create and manage digital loyalty programs (stamp cards and points systems), launch targeted marketing campaigns, and engage customers through push notifications — all from a web dashboard. Consumers use a mobile app to collect stamps/points, receive offers, and redeem rewards.

**Target market:** Worldwide, multilingual
**Business model:** Freemium + Premium (subscriptions for merchants)

---

## 2. Architecture

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                   USERS                          │
├──────────────────────┬──────────────────────────┤
│   Mobile App (Client)│  Web Dashboard (Merchant) │
│   React Native (Expo)│  Next.js + Tailwind       │
├──────────────────────┴──────────────────────────┤
│                 API Layer                         │
│        Supabase (Auth + REST + Realtime)          │
│        + Edge Functions (business logic)           │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│              Database                             │
│           PostgreSQL (Supabase)                    │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│            External Services                      │
│  Push: Expo Notifications + OneSignal             │
│  Payments: Stripe (merchant subscriptions)        │
│  Storage: Supabase Storage (logos, images)         │
│  Analytics: PostHog                               │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

**3 layers:**
1. **Mobile app** (React Native/Expo) — consumer scans, collects stamps/points, receives notifications
2. **Web dashboard** (Next.js) — merchant creates cards, launches campaigns, tracks analytics
3. **Backend** (Supabase) — auth, database, push, file storage, serverless functions

