## 3. Data Model

### Merchants
- id, name, logo, address, category, plan (free/pro/business)
- subscription_status, stripe_customer_id

### Loyalty Programs
- id, merchant_id, type (stamp | points), name
- stamp_goal, points_per_euro, reward_description
- expiration_days, is_active

### Rewards
- id, program_id, name, description
- points_cost | stamps_required
- discount_type (percentage | fixed | freebie), discount_value

### Campaigns
- id, merchant_id, title, body, image_url
- type (push | in_app | targeted_ad)
- target_segment (all | new | inactive | vip | custom)
- scheduled_at, sent_at, status
- analytics (opens, clicks, conversions)

### QR Codes / NFC Tags
- id, merchant_id, location, type (stamp | redeem)
- secret_key (secure validation)

### Customers
- id, email, name, phone, push_token
- preferred_language, location

### Customer Cards
- id, customer_id, program_id
- current_stamps | current_points
- tier (bronze | silver | gold | vip)
- created_at, last_activity

### Transactions
- id, card_id, type (stamp_add | points_add | reward_redeem)
- value, validated_by (qr | nfc | manual)
- created_at

### Referrals
- id, referrer_id, referred_id, merchant_id
- reward_given, status, created_at

### Notifications
- id, customer_id, campaign_id, title, body
- type (campaign | reward_available | expiration_warning | proximity)
- read_at, sent_at, deep_link

