## 6. Push Notifications

| Type | Trigger |
|------|---------|
| Campaign offer | Merchant launches manually |
| Inactivity reminder | Auto after X days without visit |
| Reward available | Auto when threshold reached |
| Expiration warning | Auto X days before points/stamps expire |
| Proximity | Auto when client near partner store |
| Welcome | Auto on registration |
| Referral | Auto when referral signs up |

